Manila rejects China claim over Scarborough Shoal . Philippine President Fidel Ramos on Wednesday rejected China ' s claim over Scarborough Shoal , a 16 - km ( 10 - mile ) rock formation in the South China Sea on which Filipinos have hoisted the country ' s flag . China recently protested against the flying of the Philippine flag on the disputed rock , calling the act a " serious violation " of China ' s sovereignty over the area . 
